15:22.880 --> 15:24.320
Do you want to support the host?

15:24.320 --> 15:26.080
Or do you want to support the device?

15:26.080 --> 15:32.640
We can start to engage with it where we're at, but meet in this kind of common project.

15:32.640 --> 15:41.720
And obviously, the goal then is to sustain open source digital infrastructure and expand

15:41.720 --> 15:43.720
cooperation.

